  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK587">
<l>maṟaintavai kēṭkavaṟ ṟāki yaṟintavai </l>
<l> yaiyappā ṭillatē yoṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A spy is one who is able to discover what is hidden and who retains no doubt concerning what he has known.</l>
            </lg>
